{"experiment_id": "synthetic_benign", "epoch": 9, "role": "user", "artifact_class": "Commit", "identifier": ["golang", "go", "53b836a0cb3c301745b64c6f79bbd51cba453bfc"], "url": "https://github.com/golang/go/commit/53b836a0cb3c301745b64c6f79bbd51cba453bfc", "semantic_text": "Request DEC mode 1036 (Alt+char sends ESC) (#201)\n\nxterm defaults to an 8-bit character encoding for Alt+key presses.\n\nPrivate mode 1036 enables the `metaSendsEscape` resource:\n\nPs = 1 0 3 6  \u21d2  Send ESC   when Meta modifies a key, xterm.\n\nCloses #197", "semantic_meaning": null, "semantic_ref": null, "semantic_label": "benign", "semantic_content_type": "real", "timestamp": 1634505283.0}
